Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.83,0:00:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓它陷入了靜寂而永恆的睡眠中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.50,0:00:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那個森林即使是現在仍然遍佈著堅硬的荊棘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷地阻止著來自外部的侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.85,0:00:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 會持續到我死亡的時候為止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.99,0:01:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)}荊棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.98,0:02:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人她…？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.32,0:02:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.09,0:02:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.18,0:02:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考試結束後就是聖誕節呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.42,0:02:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃薔薇大人說結業式時要在薔薇館開個聯歡會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有甚麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.82,0:02:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.07,0:02:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜歡聖誕節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要包裝嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.17,0:02:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是流言中的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.93,0:02:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是放棄讀這本書比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.49,0:02:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.45,0:02:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳怎麼想呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我的話 會讀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一方面也有些在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先單純地讀讀看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.91,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎樣去讀 如果白薔薇大人的事真寫在上面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.67,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.68,0:03:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,須加星如果是白薔薇大人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.95,0:03:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概我會更加尊敬她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會請她在文集上簽名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不錯啊 你的這種性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.11,0:03:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 果然對是否讀這本書猶豫不決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荊棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這本書的作者「須加星」實際上是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.06,0:03:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.89,0:03:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 那個白薔薇大人出版了將自已\n隱藏的過去毫不隱瞞地拼綴起來的自白小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種流言在到處流傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.94,0:03:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說也只是流言而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.21,0:03:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些看過這本叫「大波斯菊通信」的\n新刊導讀雜誌上專題介紹的人們的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荊棘的森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作者 須加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.12,0:04:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在學園裡數月的生活是否只是夢幻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.28,0:04:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖將一切封印在了心中那荊棘的森林中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.98,0:04:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人期待的新人作家 衝擊的自傳性處女作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,須加星與白薔薇大人的真名「佐藤聖」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確「星」與「聖」發音相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且既然是自傳性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是將自已的過去寫在了這本小說裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家會流言四起也是可以理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人過去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.27,0:04:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為一年級生的由乃你們大概不知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.58,0:04:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人的過去也可說是禁忌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.25,0:04:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都儘量不去提及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可說是一種「無言的理解」吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道事情的人大家都三緘其口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像在保護著甚麼似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是發生了甚麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.20,0:05:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時我是一年級生 沒有被告知詳細的經過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.26,0:05:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去… 是去年的事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.82,0:05:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.94,0:05:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那個白薔薇大人的過去寫在了這本書裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人會猶豫也是不無道理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.86,0:05:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊 大人們想強制把互為摯友的聖與香織分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.73,0:05:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是她們在聖誕夜裡踏上了沒有目的地的旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然她們兩人想一起死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但當聖在病院裡醒過來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香織已經去往天國了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很常見的結局嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.02,0:05:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學 你看到最後都沒哭嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.53,0:05:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得有些地方和我與祥子大人很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.46,0:05:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 想說的不是小說的內容啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確看了這個後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.58,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有流言說作者是白薔薇大人倒也可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.18,0:06:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為小說的舞台只可能是莉莉安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊 令雖然也看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.26,0:06:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就說「不要再插手這件事」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.14,0:06:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.96,0:06:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「就當沒有讀過這本小說」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.16,0:06:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「完全不想與流言有任何關聯」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.41,0:06:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 祥子大人在買了文集後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺也是對讀還是不讀猶豫不決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.98,0:06:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了甚麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令甚麼也不肯對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.22,0:06:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 只有直接去問白薔薇大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.97,0:06:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.61,0:06:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是只有去問白薔薇大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.26,0:07:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 志摩子同學也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼…？ 你們不是姐妹嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在意嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在就去比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.17,0:07:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.10,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點的話 白薔薇大人就會去薔薇館了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.29,0:07:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在令大人與祥子大人面前問不出口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年級藤組 佐藤聖同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請立刻到生活指導室來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說是因為那本小說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 祐巳也被傳喚了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.68,0:07:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.01,0:07:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是祐巳將我作為「摟抱魔」告發了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.37,0:08:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人 您還不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我本來還想問您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.24,0:08:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「荊棘的森林」的作者\n是否就是白薔薇大人您或是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.74,0:08:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荊棘？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.83,0:08:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下去的話一會兒再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.56,0:08:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園長 中高等部校長 年級主任以及藤組的負責人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.27,0:08:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「荊棘的森林」已經變成這麼嚴重的問題了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.06,0:08:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是跟往常一樣開朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.46,0:08:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好像還不知道被傳喚的原因呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.03,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.67,0:08:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.55,0:09:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是值得告訴新聞部的東西 我們可是一點兒也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.16,0:09:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說 幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人退學也無所謂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.54,0:09:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的學園可是禁止打工的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.56,0:09:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫小說甚麼的明顯是違反了校規啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.01,0:09:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退學甚麼的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.78,0:09:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果事情變成那樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.30,0:09:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用「莉莉安瓦版」來發起署名活動也無所謂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.24,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫上「請不要將白薔薇大人退學」甚麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.69,0:09:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我們真的甚麼也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.61,0:09:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.72,0:09:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒法再支撐下去了 快站好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.16,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 在生活指導室裡互相抱著摔在一起可不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.78,0:10:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉打擾到各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.78,0:10:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.81,0:10:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮到\n大家無法抑制的好奇心我還是先報告一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.97,0:10:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾 寫「荊棘的森林」的人不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.08,0:10:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 這一次不能向\n莉莉安瓦版提供新聞材料真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,築山三奈子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪裡啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是薔薇館了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概大家聽到傳喚的廣播後都在等我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相當華麗的傳喚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是從沒有因個人的事情而被傳喚過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.14,0:10:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有點羡慕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.59,0:10:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是不敢當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是薔薇大人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒像我這樣慌裡慌張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了生活指導室嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.23,0:11:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.16,0:11:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.72,0:11:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.13,0:11:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上等品真是不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我先報告一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.93,0:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經向祐巳與由乃說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流言中的那本小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.37,0:11:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是被傳喚的原因嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.28,0:11:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚地說明不是我寫的之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園長為我說了好話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後簡單地就讓我離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.03,0:11:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自已既沒有讀過實物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.63,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且對於那個流傳的謠言也是剛才才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不是你寫的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向聖母瑪莉亞發誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個話題就到此結束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.88,0:12:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？ 黃薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.56,0:12:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有異議 紅薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 該討論一下聖誕節的聯歡會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.92,0:12:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.17,0:12:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都未受到流言的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.94,0:12:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還真是自我中心又淺薄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.65,0:12:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情低落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.05,0:12:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我臉上的表情又變來變去了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想發言嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.95,0:12:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要睡得迷迷糊糊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.96,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意見的人要好好地舉起手來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.53,0:12:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟會為了這種人而煩惱真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請住手 白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.39,0:13:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 在鬧情緒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子 把祐巳借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒是沒甚麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.85,0:13:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會脫她的制服或是胡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再開玩笑的話 我可要拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.95,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令 把由乃也借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要由乃願意的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.64,0:13:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼痛快就允諾沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.94,0:13:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為令明白我不會對由乃淘氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那為甚麼只對我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為反應很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 祥子的反應也很讓人開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.19,0:13:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是一次捉弄就會有雙倍樂趣的姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.73,0:13:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.05,0:13:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.03,0:13:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我成了壞心前輩的餌食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 後面的收拾就由我們三人來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.23,0:14:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家請先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼後面就拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.13,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.53,0:14:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 不要讓白薔薇大人太開心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.32,0:14:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 有需要我幫忙的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.82,0:14:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在看起來也沒甚麼需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.87,0:14:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.29,0:14:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我就先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們陪著姐姐真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.89,0:14:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.29,0:14:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓志摩子同學跟我們在一起不行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子是那種即使跟她說不要留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要她想留下來就會憑自已的意志留下來的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.25,0:14:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.94,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在帶著那本「荊棘的森林」嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.12,0:14:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能借我一下嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.69,0:15:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借倒是沒甚麼問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您想做甚麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.82,0:15:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是讀它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.72,0:15:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你以為我會拿它當鍋墊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.53,0:15:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼做為回禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.62,0:15:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面食堂的餐券？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.71,0:15:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.85,0:15:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來的時候在自動販賣機那裡幫我買一罐咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連你們的份也一起買好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.42,0:15:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人真是個不可預料的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.12,0:15:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子同學真是了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.86,0:15:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟能和那種人做姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.92,0:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在頸上圍上手帕比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣領會弄髒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.99,0:15:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.79,0:15:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.36,0:15:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人究竟是為了甚麼將我們留下來呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.69,0:15:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 如果只是為了借「荊棘的森林」的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接帶回家去不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.82,0:15:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.21,0:16:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是因為我們太可愛 所以想要請我們吃拉麵嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同學 腦筋快成豆腐渣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般來說是不會買罐裝年糕豆湯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.98,0:16:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒甚麼關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.58,0:16:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 那個罐裝年糕豆湯甚麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同學買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.57,0:16:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世界上還有這種東西存在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.95,0:16:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 白薔薇大人要的咖啡我們可是好好地買來了喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經把書仔細地讀完了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讀了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.65,0:16:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認為「荊棘的森林」是我寫的\N那些人也許真是有很好的直覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.75,0:16:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不是跟我很像嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.04,0:16:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們想問也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.31,0:17:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家會認為寫那本小說的是我的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅僅是名字同音而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一點你們也應該有些發覺了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.64,0:17:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們毫不掩飾地流露出了那種好奇心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不是為了看你們這種表情才說這種話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.52,0:17:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想說的部份我不會說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.38,0:17:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也沒問題的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.08,0:17:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為總覺得只有你們不知道不是很不公平嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.76,0:17:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了告訴我們才將我們留下來的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然也是為了想早點讀到這本書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.96,0:17:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓉子與令她們之所以不向你們說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也許是為了體諒我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那麼痛苦的事情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾有過一個非常要好的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.22,0:17:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說她甚至比父母和兄弟更加重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.14,0:17:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡她到只要有她在 其它甚麼也不需要的地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一個想著將來成為修女的純潔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.71,0:18:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 在去年的聖誕節裡 她離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.37,0:18:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完完全全是「荊棘的森林」的聖與香織嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.49,0:18:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是完全相同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.25,0:18:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我既沒有與那個朋友一起踏上旅途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.15,0:18:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有吞下安眠藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她轉學了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.47,0:18:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說香織還活著了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.97,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚麼呀 還活著很失望嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.48,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 難道是誰以白薔薇大人\N的事作為參考而寫下了這本小說嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.87,0:18:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.63,0:18:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既有不同的部份 也有相似得驚人的部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.73,0:18:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不覺得生氣嗎 白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自已的過去被擅自寫成了小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還被人誤認為是作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.70,0:18:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 只要能被最重要的人理解就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才想講給你們倆聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.09,0:19:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我討厭殘留著誤解與臆測的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.82,0:19:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉學的朋友 現在怎麼樣了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.28,0:19:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.23,0:19:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想見她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不見面 為好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.86,0:19:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人的名字 不是香織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs52}而是久保 {\fs39\fnsimhei}栞{\r}…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.50,0:19:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白薔薇大人現在還喜歡著那個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也這樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才沒有留下志摩子同學吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為會對志摩子同學很過意不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.73,0:19:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.82,0:19:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明會有因小說而受到傷害的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫那本小說的不會是久保{\fs39\fnsimhei}栞{\r}吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.17,0:20:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.06,0:20:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會徹底查明寫這本「荊棘的森林」的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.85,0:20:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是大波斯菊編輯部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為甚麼要把我也拉來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令也很在意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.05,0:20:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「荊棘的森林」的作者到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.63,0:20:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.06,0:20:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉在忙碌的時候來打擾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問 你是「荊棘的森林」的負責人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.99,0:20:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我不能將須加星的真實身份告訴你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.99,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾天 來自莉莉安學生們的詢問接連不斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.18,0:20:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「須加星的真實身份是否是佐藤聖」之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老…老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.43,0:20:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真令人懷念啊 這種制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到會在這種地方遇到後輩們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.53,0:21:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.78,0:21:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這麼說您是莉莉安的畢業生了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.19,0:21:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是很久以前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.12,0:21:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.93,0:21:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.53,0:21:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是須加星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本名是春日誠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.08,0:21:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼「荊棘的森林」的舞台果然是莉莉安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前發生的事情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.53,0:21:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「荊棘的森林」是在如今\n連傳聞都未留下的很久以前發生的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.97,0:21:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟白薔薇大人的故事就像是其它的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.48,0:21:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒有從嘴裡說出她的名字了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.31,0:21:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新生嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.14,0:21:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.94,0:22:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今年開始進入莉莉安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.48,0:22:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.73,0:23:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 花瓣的瓣是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.03,0:23:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個「瓣」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.62,0:23:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老是拘泥在一些古怪的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.64,0:23:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花瓣的瓣寫成漢字就是便當的「便」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.64,0:23:28.34,topfont,NTP,0,0,0,,注：日語中花瓣的「瓣」與便當的「便」同形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.36,0:23:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便當的「便」嗎 原來如此 是便當的「便」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.45,0:23:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周明明是個好故事 真覺得有點被糟塌啦
